1. Since the latest PHP 5.3.9-RC4 has fixed this issue, so for 5.3 you can upgrade to 5.3.9RC4
   Of course if you don't want to upgrade to a RC version, you can simply tweak this patch into a 5.3 suitable patch.
2. Plz apply this patch after configured, this patch change the version literal number in main/php_version.h(generated by configure)
